title: Macadamia nut and coconut squares
ingredients: ['225g butter', '450g dark brown soft sugar, divided', '1 tablespoon instant coffee powder', '1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '250g plain flour', '3 eggs', '2 teaspoons vanilla extract', '150g desiccated coconut', '275g chopped and toasted macadamia nuts']
